commonPatterns:
Control strip with dispatch by command:
public void init() {
  add(new JButton("Start"), SOUTH);
  add(new JButton("Stop"), SOUTH);
  addActionListeners();
}
public void actionPerformed(ActionEvent e) {
  switch (e.getActionCommand()) {
    case "Start": start(); break;
    case "Stop": stop(); break;
  }
}

Text field and Enter mirrors button action:
public void init() {
  nameField = new JTextField(12);
  add(nameField, SOUTH);
  add(new JButton("Greet"), SOUTH);
  addActionListeners();
  nameField.addActionListener(this);
}
public void actionPerformed(ActionEvent e) {
  if (e.getActionCommand().equals("Greet") || e.getSource() == nameField) greet();
}

